---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout locale="zh" title="页面未找到 | LONFRO">
  <section class="page-hero not-found">
    <div class="container narrow-heading">
      <h1>未找到该页面。</h1>
      <p>该产品或页面可能已移动。您可浏览当前产品目录，或联系我们获取帮助。</p>
      <div class="hero-actions"><a class="button button-primary" href="/zh/products/">浏览产品</a><a class="button button-secondary" href="/zh/contact/">联系我们</a></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
